name: K2 surveillance
description:
The K2 surveillance of the Allied Army in Area 51 is monitoring and spying on aliens around the clock.
The axial thrust of k2 with nuclear fuel is ready to launch k2 deep into the galaxy. Under the command of the empire, General Hypota has full control over the invaders with spy equipment and drones, and provides encrypted information to the defense forces on an instantaneous basis.
